                    <h4 style="text-align:left; ">Gridcoin Introduction</h4>
                    <p>The following guides explain how to set up the Gridcoin Research wallet client on the platform of your choice.</p>
                    <p>
                        If you want to run Gridcoin in investor-mode only, you do not need to install the BOINC client. In this case, you will only earn POS interest and not recieve DPOR payments due to a lack of BOINC research. The amount and frequency of interest depends on the quantity of coins you are holding in your wallet/client.
                    </p>
